high_descs: Walk over to the stove to your left.
Pick up the pan on the stove.
Turn around and walk to the counter to your left.
Place the pan on the counter next to the tomato.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Put the tomato on the pan.
anns.task_desc: Place pan on the counter with a tomato on it.

high_descs: Pick up pan from back right burner.
Turn left, proceed to counter next to sink.
Place pan on left hand corner of counter, left and forward of tomato.
Place tomato in the pan on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move pan to counter, place tomato in pan.

high_descs: Cross the room to the stove ahead of you
Grab the pan that is on the right back burner
Turn to the right and head to the sink
Place the pan on the counter to the left of the sink
Pick up the tomato that is sitting on the counter to the left of the sink
Place the tomato into the pan
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato into a pan
